headline: VICI Properties Inc. Announces Release Date for Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Results
summary: NEW YORK, January 02, 2025--VICI Properties Inc. (NYSE: VICI) ("VICI Properties" or the "Company") announced today that it will release its fourth quarter and full year 2024 financial results on Thursday, February 20, 2025 after the close of trading on the New York Stock Exchange. The Company will host a conference call and audio webcast on Friday, February 21, 2025 at 10:00 a.m. Eastern Time (ET).
